data.description:
We have received multiple offers, please have your highest and best in no later than Wednesday, December 20, 2023 at 7pm, we will respond but 9pm.  Seller has the right to accept an offer prior to this deadline.  
Thank you for showing!North Newark, ranch home with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Family bath completely updated November 2018. Open foyer entry, that takes you to the formal living room and dining room combined. Chandelier in dining room will be replaced. Eat in kitchen, completely updated floors, ceiling, cabinets, lighting, appliances, June 2019, with granite countertops, stainless steel appliance and wine refrigerator. Family room with bay window. The mud room leading to 2 car attached garage. Laminate flooring, trim and interior doors replaced 2019. Off of the kitchen, exit out onto a screened in back porch with patio. Backyard and storage shed. Walking distance to Hillview Elementary, close to Trout Club. Washer, dryer and deep freezer do convey.  Hot tub does not convey. One year home warranty included.
